<F P=106> [Unattributed newsbrief under the "In Brief" Rubric] </F>
  [Text] SARATOV. Between the 28th of December and the 21st 
of January, 74 cases of diptheria were reported in the Saratov 
oblast, including 18 cases involving children. As of January 
23rd, six people, including three children, had died of the 
disease. 

</TEXT>

