<H3> <TI>   Penalty Backed for `Irresponsible' HIV Infection </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Penalty Backed for `Irresponsible' HIV Infection </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    Cabinet Gives Go-Ahead </H4>

<F P=102> 94WE0248E Copenhagen BERLINGSKE TIDENDE in Danish 20 Apr 94 
p 4 </F>

<F P=103> 94WE0248E </F>
<F P=104>  Copenhagen BERLINGSKE TIDENDE </F>
<F P=105>  Danish </F>


