<H3> <TI>   F-16's to Pakistan Justify Proliferation Stand </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    F-16's to Pakistan Justify Proliferation Stand </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    NPT Acceptance `Unlikely' </H4>

<F P=102> 94WP0087B Bombay THE TIMES OF INDIA in English 22 Mar 94 p 16 </F>
<F P=103> 94WP0087B </F>
<F P=104>  Bombay THE TIMES OF INDIA </F>
