  [Text] REUTER cites fundamentalist officials in Beirut as 
saying that members of their group are preparing to launch a 
spectacular operation against the Israelis to avenge the 
kidnapping of Mustafa al-Dirani, military official in charge of 
the so-called Believers Group, in al-Biqa' at dawn yesterday. 

