Brig. Gen. Doron Almog from traveling freely on roads in the 
Gaza Strip has been brought to trial and sent to jail. IDF 
[Israel Defense Forces] sources this morning expressed 
satisfaction about the way Palestinian police roadblocks 
checking Palestinians at the border crossings with Israel have 
been working. 

