<H3> <TI>   Kakh Activists Remanded in Administrative Detention </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Kakh Activists Remanded in Administrative Detention </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   TA2305125094 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in Hebrew 1200 GMT 23 
