  [Text] A stabbing in Jerusalem: A short time ago, an Arab 
stabbed a yeshiva student on Hanevi'im Street, near the 
east-west divide, slightly wounding him. The assailant fled the 
scene, and a manhunt is currently under way. This is an initial 
report by our police affairs correspondent Aviv Bushinsky. 

</TEXT>

