<H3> <TI>   New Palestinian Group Attacks IDF Post in South </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    New Palestinian Group Attacks IDF Post in South </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   NC2105185894 Tehran Voice of the Islamic Republic of Iran in 
Arabic 1730 GMT 21 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> NC2105185894 </F>
