<H4>    Further on Helicopter Takeoff </H4>

<F P=102> LD2705070394 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 0647 GMT 27 May 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD2705070394 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow ITAR-TASS </F>
