<H3> <TI>   Dniester Procurator Injured in Assassination Attempt </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Dniester Procurator Injured in Assassination Attempt </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    `Radio-Controlled' Device Used </H4>

<F P=102> LD2705111194 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service in Russian 1001 
GMT 27 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2705111194 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [By ITAR-TASS correspondent Valeriy Demidetskiy] </F>
  [Text] Kishinev [Chisinau], 27 May -- An assassination 
attempt has been made on Boris Luchik, the procurator of the 
Dniester Republic. Yesterday evening, when he and his wife 
entered their house accompanied by guards, a powerful explosion 
was heard near the lift. The procurator's wife perished, 
doctors are struggling to save the lives of Boris Luchik and his 
guards. 
  It was reported to the ITAR-TASS correspondent today by Oleg 
Gudym, acting minister of state security of the Dniester 
Republic, that the explosion was carried out with the help of a 
radio-controlled device. 

</TEXT>

