<H4>    Presidency Denies Suspension </H4>

<F P=102> PA2805231994 Santa Fe de Bogota Emisoras Caracol Network in 
Spanish 2302 GMT 28 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> PA2805231994 </F>
<F P=104>  Santa Fe de Bogota Emisoras Caracol Network </F>
<F P=105>  Spanish </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [Press communique issued by the Colombian Presidency in </F>
Santa Fe de Bogota on 28 May; from the "Quarter of an Hour 
Caracol" news segment] 
  [Text] Given various news reports that elections have been 
suspended in some corregimientos, the government hereby informs 
the public that elections have not been suspended anywhere in 
the territory. Election preparations are under way throughout 
the country. 
  [Issued in] Santa Fe de Bogota, Capital District 
  [Dated] 28 May 1994 

</TEXT>

